# Discord links (rate-limited, always returns 403 for bots)
https://discord.gg/*

# Shields.io badges (sometimes flaky under load)
https://img.shields.io/*

# Crates.io (rate-limited)
https://crates.io/*

# Docs.rs (build-dependent, links may not exist until published)
https://docs.rs/*

# GitHub Actions marketplace (requires auth)
https://github.com/marketplace/*

# Local/development URLs
http://localhost:*
http://127.0.0.1:*

# Placeholder links in templates
https://example.com/*

# kimberlite.dev — documentation site not yet live. Docs reference the
# future canonical URLs; ignore until the site ships.
https://kimberlite.dev/*
https://incidents.kimberlite.dev/*
https://status.kimberlite.dev/*

# Illustrative / aspirational URLs used in operating runbooks
https://pagerduty.com/kimberlite-production

# Upstream bincode spec was moved; docs reference the old path for
# historical context. Covered by a note in the doc itself.
https://github.com/bincode-org/bincode/blob/trunk/docs/spec.md
